title: Jacksonville State vs. Florida State Condensed Game | 2021 ACC Football
author: ACC Digital Network
description:
Coming off a short week, the Florida State Seminoles lost to Jacksonville State, 20-17, on a Hail Mary as the clock expired.  Seminoles quarterback Jashaun Corbin rushed for 109 yards on 15 carries and scored a touchdown.  The Seminoles rushed for 202 yards total on the game.
